release.changelog:
Hello to AI-powered Neptune Browser!
* You can now open the AI model as a half-window from the shortcut menu on the main screen. You can change the model you want to use from the settings.
* You can now save, view, or edit any website to Bookmarks via the dropdown menu.
* You can now view or clear the Browser History via the dropdown menu.
